e4a9c77","tid":1462471,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"少人=宣傳<br />\n多人=癱瘓"},{"pid":"acd57fbe36431ca439173255a735498c28c1e2ee","tid":1462471,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"a3e7c534942e2e28039735ef6d773992749282a9","tid":1462471,"uid":287449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得要隔日塞比一日人地番屋企，將心比心，你可以忍耐一班被迫壓既人阻左你一日番屋企，都應該忍唔到比人阻左成個星期都番唔到屋企掛？<br />\n依家塞機場個重點係影響<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">經濟</span></strong>，唔係要影響旅客<br />\n<br />\n隔日塞一樣好嚴重影響經濟，但係旅客都只係遲左一日半日番屋企，冇咁不滿又可以達到影響經濟既效果，仲可以比我地自己抖下<br />\n<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dCQMBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dCQMBS</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好比衝動同憤怒控制自己"},{"pid":"db78e3d2c1f07ec0d6216032e0139931eb8c8842","tid":1462471,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"究竟係衝動定有鬼呀！！！<br />\n搵人去搞搞佢唔好阻住人出境啦<br />\n國際笑話喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd371ee2ba80584aad57c12629a8749e32649238","tid":1462471,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"880554b5fa37f4235bc7101fd923a0a07730135b","tid":1462471,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}